                <head>No. 640<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On April 2, the United States and Japan signed at Tokyo a Treaty of Friendship,
                    Commerce and Navigation, with Protocol. For text, see 4 <gloss target="#t_UST1"
                        >UST</gloss> (pt. 2) 2063.</p>
                <p>Documents concerning the negotiation of this treaty are principally in file
                    611.944 for 1952–1953.</p>
            </div>
